%header
  =render partial: 'layouts/header'

  - @product.each do |product|
    .example-btn
      = link_to "/products/#{product.id}", method: :get do
        = product.name
  %end

%main
  %section.mainVisual
    .mainVisual__contents
      %h2.mainVisual__contents__subtitle 人生を変えるフリマアプリ
      %p.mainVisual__contents__text FURIMAはだれでもかんたんに出品・購入できる<br>フリマアプリです
      .appLink
        .appLink__appleStore__btn
          = link_to 'https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/apple-store/id375380948?mt=8' do
            = image_tag 'app-store-9c5e28e8f81bd9912e0ded2f78821e04778a1356c05dc7c7bf1e88614be37c34.svg', width: '150'
        .appLink__googlePley__btn
          = link_to 'https://play.google.com/store/apps?pcampaignid=pcampaignidMKT-Other-global-all-co-prtnr-py-PartBadge-Mar2515-1' do
            = image_tag 'https://play.google.com/intl/ja/badges/static/images/badges/ja_badge_web_generic.png', width: '165'

  %section.topIntroduction
    %h2.topIntroduction__subtitle FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
    .topIntroduction__contents
      %ul.topIntroduction__contents__lists
        %li.topIntroduction__contents__lists__firstBox
          .topIntroduction__contents__lists__firstBox__pict
            %span.topIntroduction__contents__lists__firstBox__pict__number 1
            = image_tag 'pict-reason-01.jpg', class: 'topIntroduction__contents__lists__firstBox__pict__img'
          %h3.topIntroduction__contents__lists__firstBox__text
            %span 3分
            ですぐに出品
          %p.topIntroduction__contents__lists__firstBox__description スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
        %li.topIntroduction__contents__lists__secondBox
          .topIntroduction__contents__lists__secondBox__pict
            %span.topIntroduction__contents__lists__secondBox__pict__number 2
            = image_tag 'pict-reason-02.jpg', class: 'topIntroduction__contents__lists__secondBox__pict__img'
          %h3.topIntroduction__contents__lists__secondBox__text
            %span シンプル
            で使いやすい
          %p.topIntroduction__contents__lists__secondBox__description めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
        %li.topIntroduction__contents__lists__thirdBox
          .topIntroduction__contents__lists__thirdBox__pict
            %span.topIntroduction__contents__lists__thirdBox__pict__number 3
            = image_tag 'pict-reason-03.jpg', class: 'topIntroduction__contents__lists__thirdBox__pict__img'
          %h3.topIntroduction__contents__lists__thirdBox__text
            手数料
            %span 業界最安値
          %p.topIntroduction__contents__lists__thirdBox__description 最大3%でお得に出品＆購入！

  %section.topMiddleDl
    .topMiddleDl__contents
      %h2.topMiddleDl__contents__subtitle 会員数世界一位
      %p.topMiddleDl__contents__text FURIMAは、フリマアプリで最も人気！<br>出品・購入回数も業界最多です！<br>ほしかったあの商品に出会えるかもしれません。
      .appLink
        .appLink__appleStore__btn
          = link_to 'https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/apple-store/id375380948?mt=8' do
            = image_tag 'app-store-9c5e28e8f81bd9912e0ded2f78821e04778a1356c05dc7c7bf1e88614be37c34.svg', width: '150'
        .appLink__googlePley__btn
          = link_to 'https://play.google.com/store/apps?pcampaignid=pcampaignidMKT-Other-global-all-co-prtnr-py-PartBadge-Mar2515-1' do
            = image_tag 'https://play.google.com/intl/ja/badges/static/images/badges/ja_badge_web_generic.png', width: '165'




  %section.topKeyFeatures
  %section.pickupContainer
  %section.pickupContainer

%footer
  =render partial: 'layouts/footer'
